name: Tsunemori Akane (Psycho-Pass)
description:
V2 Description

I feel first version wasn't that bad, but this one should be more compatible, works on weight 1 and separated outfits better. Prompts that I used are:

Regular suit - tsunemori akane, black jacket, dress shirt, pencil skirt. black skirt, pantyhose

More badass - tsunemori akane, black jacket, white shirt, open jacket, pencil skirt. black skirt, pantyhose

Blue jacket - tsunemori akane, blue jacket, open jacket, dress shirt, clothes writing, pencil skirt, black skirt, pantyhose

Movie version - tsunemori akane, bulletproof vest, white shirt, clothes writing, fingerless gloves, belt, blue pants, combat boots

Like before, you can use gun, holding gun to maybe get something that slightly resembles dominator. I feel V1 might have actually did that better.

V1 Description

Lora model for Tsunemori Akane from Psycho-Pass.

Use tsunemori akane phrase and weight between 0.7-0.9. For right outfit try suit jacket, collared shirt, pencil skirt. If you'll be trying to give her more boyish clothes, better add 1girl to avoid surprises since she can look boyish herself sometimes. Or don't, add 1boy if you want and see where that takes you. If you add gun, holding gun you will get something resembling dominator, but it wasn't really trained for that.

military, military uniform gets cool results similiar to movie outfit.
